TM1py Documentation¶

Module contents¶

A python module for TM1.

https://github.com/cubewise-code/TM1py

TM1py wraps the TM1 REST API into concise Python classes and Services that simplify TM1 interactions from python.

Usage: >>> with RestService(address=’’, port=8001, user=’admin’, password=’apple’, ssl=False) as tm1_rest: >>> subset_service = SubsetService(tm1_rest) >>> subset = Subset(dimension_name=’Month’, subset_name=’Q1’, elements=[‘Jan’, ‘Feb’, ‘Mar’]) >>> subset_service.create(subset, private=True)
